### Conversations API Test File
### Ersetze {{token}} mit einem gültigen JWT Token (aus auth.http)

@apiUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get all conversations for current user
GET {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get conversations with pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new conversation (with listing)
POST {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listingId": "YOUR_LISTING_ID_HERE",
  "participantIds": ["USER_ID_1", "USER_ID_2"]
}

### Create a new conversation (direct chat, no listing)
POST {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantIds": ["USER_ID_1", "USER_ID_2"]
}

### Get messages for a conversation
GET {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get messages with pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE/messages?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send a message
POST {{apiUrl}}/api/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID_HERE/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hallo! Ist das Angebot noch verfügbar?"
}

